1553112112.content:
Emma invited Regina, Zelena, Snow, and Belle to her house to hang out. Regina knocks on the door. "Come in." Emma shouts. They walk in and find Emma in her living room.

There on the floor was Emma, wearing nothing but a diaper with the Swan Queen on them and a baby shirt with the same design. "Emma?!" Snow asked shocked. "Guys!...I..I" Emma started but couldn't really think of a way to explain. "Um...as you can see I like diapers."

"It’s okay Emma I like diapers too." said Regina. "Me too." the others said in unison. "Let’s get our diapers out." Zelena suggested.

They all get their diapers. Regina poofs her Evil Queen diapers in her hand. Zelena gets out her Wicked Witch of the West. Snow pulls out her Snow White diapers. Belle grabs her Belle diapers out of her bag. Emma thinks for a minute because she is not a famous character and she finally picks Swan Queen diapers.

Then Regina uses her magic to put everyone in their diapers and matching baby shirt.

They are all sitting on the floor and Emma has an idea. "Hey we should get Ruby to be our mommy." Everyone agrees and Emma calls Ruby.

Ruby comes over and they explain the situation. Ruby agrees and then they all get hungry.
1553112112.title: Emma in Diapers at Home
